"```sql\nSELECT AVG(s.NumTstTakr) AS AverageTestTakers\nFROM satscores s\nJOIN schools sch ON s.cds = sch.CDSCode\nWHERE sch.County = 'Fresno'\n  AND YEAR(sch.OpenDate) = 1980;\n```\n\nThis SQL query calculates the average number of SAT test takers from schools in Fresno County that opened in the year 1980. It joins the `satscores` table with the `schools` table using the `CDSCode` as the foreign key and filters the results based on the county and the opening year of the schools."